description:
This is a 27 minute workout called '20 Minute Bodyweight Strength Workout [FULL BODY // No Equipment]' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Tap in  to this 20 Minute strength workout that requires NO equipment. This full body flow is has a mixture of active movements and isometric holds to help you maximize strength and stability. This workout is great for advanced through beginners and there are modifications mixed in to help you manage through the workout . This workout is great for building strength, stability, muscle mass, and it can even be used as a recovery day workout for heavy lifters. customize this workout to your needs and be sure to comment  how your workout went!
